voca.means_en: Don't you get stuck in a heavy traffic jam every morning?\nDon't you feel dizzy now?\n
I am not used to having food in the morning.\n
What could I get you tonight?\n

voca.pattern: Do you mind if I + V ?
voca.means_en: Do you mind if I sit here?\n
I have to get to the library.\n

voca.means_ko: ~ 인지 보이지 않아요.\n~ 인지 그렇게 생각하지 않아요.
voca.means_en: I don’t see what the big deal is.\n
I learned that summer vacation had just started.\n
Yeah. How about Curse of the Mummy's Breath? Talk about not brushing your teeth…\n

voca.means_ko: ~ 하다면 내가 알고 있을거에요.\n~ 했다면 내가 알고 있었을 거에요.
voca.means_en: I would know if I bought something that expensive.\n
